title: Toronto's Babcock makes first NHL coach's challenge
text: Toronto's Babcock makes first NHL coach's challenge Thursday, 8 October 2015 (3 minutes ago) TORONTO (AP) The Toronto Maple Leafs' Mike Babcock made the first coach's challenge in NHL history and was successful in overturning a goal by the Montreal Canadiens. Toronto Maple Leafs' Mike Babcock became the first coach to employ one of the NHL's new rules when he successfully used the Coach's Challenge in the second...
